The orchid is almost always the most popular flower in plant markets across China. It's believed that they bring good fortune. Its wide variety and unique elegance attract many plant lovers. Its long flowering period and easy maintenance can boost the festive atmosphere of your home and add a touch of vibrant color to your house, especially during Spring Festival. (Artwork provided by Zhongshan Broadcasting and Television Station and artist Peng Zhangjun; Cover image designed by CGTN's Gao Hongmei) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)